Texas Poker (or Texas Hold'em) is definitely one of the most common and popular types of poker. A distinctive feature of Texas Poker from other types of poker is that in the betting round (flop, turn, river) common cards are putting on the table. Players create their best combination by combining (replacing) the cards that were dealt at the beginning, with the total cards on table.

